data.description: Newly Renovated! Move-in ready ranch home nestled in a serene cul-de-sac. This charming residence features 4 Bedroom, 2 Full Baths and an array of versatile space. Perfect for a first time home buyer or rental property. The spacious Gourmet Kitchen is a chef’s dream. The adjacent dining area offers a seamless flow and ideal space for everyday dining. Includes BONUS ROOM great for entertaining or man cave…Private fenced backyard with covered porch and side deck great for outdoor grilling. This is truly a must-see home.  Owner/Agent.
